Get Lost in Korea

Travel Documentary hosted by Greg Goodman, published by Channel 4 in 2013 - English narration


Information
------------------------------

Get Lost in Korea
Travel photographer Greg Goodman explores the hidden gems of Korea as he documents the country's fascinating traditions and cultures. This single-episode show chronicles my journey as I explore, photograph and blog about the hidden side of South Korea. You can expect a mix of humor, adventure, tradition and stunning imagery; as I team up with Jesse Day: a Canadian entertainer who lives in Seoul and raps in Korean. 
Highlights include catching and eating a live octopus, attending an exorcism and a day learning meditative martial arts from monks.

